ax_client = AxClient()
ax_client.create_experiment(parameters=[{'name': 'x', 'type': 'range',
    'bounds': [-5.0, 10.0]}, {'name': 'y', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [0.0,
    15.0]}], minimize=True)
batch_trial = ax_client.experiment.new_batch_trial(generator_run=
    GeneratorRun(arms=[Arm(parameters={'x': 0, 'y': 1}), Arm(parameters={
    'x': 0, 'y': 1})]))
with self.assertRaises(NotImplementedError):
    ax_client.complete_trial(batch_trial.index, 0)
